data.description: Convenience is key, and this home delivers! Proximity to the beach, shopping, dining, and military bases makes every day a breeze. Whether you're a beach enthusiast, a shopper, or a foodie, this location has something for everyone.This charming residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style with plenty of storage space. Love to cook or entertain? The kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with contemporary appliances and ample counter space. Enjoy meals with family and friends in the adjacent dining area, perfect for hosting memorable gatherings. Soak up the sun in your expansive front and back yards – an ideal setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day. The large driveway and two-car garage ensure plenty of parking space for you and your guests. Step into a beautifully updated interior featuring durable LVP throughout the living spaces and newer carpet in the bedrooms. Make this your first stop!
